ch plc lse spo for which scientific games holds a  ownership stake and on the board of overseers of columbia business school where he is also the chairman of the advisory board of the entrepreneurship center mr weil earned his undergraduate degree at the university of toronto an ms from the london school of economics and an mba from columbia university he lives with his wife kathy and two children in new york city   a personal snap shot of lorne weil ten questions for lorne weil chairman and ceo scientific games corporation q what was your first job a member of the professional staff of the boston consulting group q name a business leader you admire a the late professor peter druckerq whats the secret to business success a its not a secret the combination of talent luck and hard work but hard work is the only thing we have any control over q whats the best piece of advice you have ever receiveda when things are going well dont be fooled into confusing good luck with personal credit q what is your greatest regret in businessa none q what skills or qualities do you wish you hada patience q what are you readinga the right hand shore by christopher tilghman q what are the highs of your current job a seeing the fruits of entrepreneurial initiative q and the lows a dealing with bureaucracies of one kind or anotherq how do you achieve work life balance a make sure i have breakfast and dinner with my kids as often as possible   news           this site is optimized for explorer   above and a monitor resolution of  x  please adjust your screen accordingly interplay multimedia pty ltddisclaims all liability for information provided within lottery insiderdata supplied by named sourcesassociated press content is copyrighted by the associated press all other news articles are owned by their respective publishers lottery insider  lorne weil the daily news service the competitive edge you need insightful information about lotteries vendors and the people who lead them  click here 