 and will focus on enhancing the company’s operational performance weil was the ceo when the company was known as autotote and led the country in providing wagering machine and software services to a majority of north american racetracks when he took the post the company’s revenues were less than  million when he switched positions to company chairman the company now called scientific games following its acquisition of the country’s foremost producer of instant lottery tickets revenues topped  billion recently the company seemed to be languishing after having lost a couple of key lottery contracts so the management shakeup and particularly the return of lorne weil as a key player was warmly welcomed by investors also appreciated it appeared was the expansion of the executive staff to a threeman team lead by weil with support from chambrello and kennedy one of our key initiatives has been to expand our presence in china where we see meaningful opportunity for growth weil commented following the announcement we’ve had significant success in china in a very short period of time that said we believe the growth potential is much greater than we have realized to date we’ve determined that we need to devote significantly more senior management time and personnel to further developing our china business as the original architect of our china expansion initiatives mike chambrello is extremely wellsuited to spearhead our strategy and execution in this key jurisdiction he added david kennedy he said will be part of the expanded team that will lead scientific games in its next phase of growth i look forward to working closely with david mike our cfo jeff lipkin and the rest of our team to reinvigorate and restore growth to our business among the key growth initiatives cited by weil were become the preeminent supplier of serverbased gaming machines in both the uk and north america further develop the international instant ticket market in north america international jurisdictions and especially in china increase product sales by tailoring the company’s products to suit all retail outlets develop and deliver new content and expand utilization of the internet and interactive technologies   ray poirier email ray poirier has been a resident of las vegas and a member of the gamingtoday staff for the past  years he was more my articles idaho reviews instant racing tribe offers arena bucks for… sands china sees leisure as… more articles by ray share topics scientific games corporation sgms lorne weil ray poirier michael chambrello david l kennedy jeff lipkin top stories nevada casinos end fiscal year with…casinos in nevada won  percent more from gamblers in the fiscal year that ended in june compared with the year before for the  months from july  to june  socalled “casino win” in nevada totaled more than  billion read more las vegas airport k ahead of…mccarran international airport is reporting that it handled  more passengers in the first half of  than the first six months last year clark county officials reported that the las vegas airport logged just under m arriving and departing people in june read more mgm resorts beats q profit forecastsmgm resorts international mgm on thursday reported secondquarter net income of  million the las vegasbased company said it had profit of  cents per share earnings adjusted for nonrecurring gains came to  cents per share read more wynn resorts tops wall street q…wynn resorts ltd reports secondquarter earnings of  million on a pershare basis the las vegasbased company said it had net income of  cents earnings adjusted for nonrecurring costs and to extinguish debt were  per share read more cowboys should be the favorite for…nfl previews  based on cumulative records last year the nfc east was the kingpin of the league at  games over  producing a wild card for the first time in seven years ny giants  and the top seed in the conference dallas  read more how big is the pokies market in australia swedish casinos a